
ent-RMCJumpsuitTSEPA = tsepa uniform
  .desc = The standard uniform of a TSEPA officer.
ent-RMCJumpsuitMarineRoyal = royal crown marine uniform
  .desc = The field uniform of the royal crown marines. They have shards of light Kevlar to help protect against stabbing weapons and bullets. Onpar with similar UNMC equipment.
